# Per-deployment provisioning config — contains the WiFi PSK and a one-time
# claim credential. NEVER commit this; copy meshanics_provisioning.h.example and
# fill it in locally. The .example template is the only version that is tracked.
meshanics_provisioning.h
**/meshanics_provisioning.h

# Legacy per-device baked credentials (pre-enrollment model). The provisioned
# identity now lives in NVS; these should never appear, but guard anyway.
device_creds.h
**/device_creds.h
pinned_key.h
**/pinned_key.h
claim_config.h
**/claim_config.h

